  "description": "Oblique at its most approachable — triangle wave, gentle fold, light prism delay, slow phaser. Works as a pad foundation for chord work. Velocity-to-fold is audible here: soft playing stays clean, harder hits add harmonic grit. Good for layering under melodic content. No macros active; FOLD is the first thing to reach for.",
